    "As discussed in Sect. 3.2, there is reason to be skeptical of these estimates.",
    "However, given that we do not have other credible sources and that even a small chance of AI catastrophe is very concerning, these estimates suffice to justify the need for academic discussion on such risks and possible societal responses.Finally, while we may still be far from AGI, there is no agreed-upon theoretical reason to expect that AGI is impossible.",
